StartEmpty=Hi! I'll help you to organize channels/groups co-promotions. Add me to a group to start or type /help for more information
Help=This bot helps channels/groups administrators to promote their channels/groups by creating campaigns and sending promotional messages to all participating chats.\nAdd the bot to a chat to create or join a campaign.\n\nNote: You need to be a campaign member in order to add the target chat to the campaign.
